<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="like-conj">like <strong><em>conj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /laɪk/    美 /laɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-as">1.★ <strong>如同；像…一样 (as)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please do it like I tell you. 
请照我说的去做。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-as-if">2.★ <strong>好像；似乎 (as if)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It <strong>sounds like</strong> they don't know what's going on either.
听起来似乎他们也不知道发生了什么事。</p></div></div>